zillow.SubDescription: Watershed brings next-level living to Laurel, MD with standout amenities throughout the neighborhood and endless acres of scenic views just beyond your front door. The commuter in your family will love the convenience of nearby employers like Fort Meade and the National Business Park in addition to closeby transportation routes that offer easy access to Baltimore and Washington, D.C.
